{"tid":2406003,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【誠意推介】一套同時令人覺得沉重 又有正能量嘅紀錄片 — 日航123空難","createTime":"2021-02-13T00:08:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-23T12:37:08.000Z","uid":341313,"like":60,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"a2858576f7e3dec5c0460fb53e186c3384990c12","tid":2406003,"uid":341313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T00:08:13.000Z","msg":"最近見到有post講日航空難<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2401734\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2401734</a><br />\n之後睇返啲紀錄片 發現呢段做得好好<br />\n睇完真係好心噏 但值得一睇<br />\n因為佢地走出傷痛嘅過程真係好感動<br />\n<br />\n首先請原諒係殘體字幕 但我只係搵到呢條<br />\n其次係如果大家想自己慢慢發掘條片嘅內容 請無視我下面嗰堆介紹 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=z_16HZtfwI0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dz_16HZtfwI0&d=kdQtjCisvz5VKkzPdH2zQ98yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=680a8b7f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=z_16HZtfwI0</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qYIqrRuGUKo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DqYIqrRuGUKo&d=kdQtjCisvz5VKkzPdH2zQ98yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=3511b525\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qYIqrRuGUKo</a><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n段片係用「事故紀錄片+情境重演+三十年後訪問」嘅形式，講返四個遇難者家庭喺出事後33年嘅生活。<br />\n講佢地當年點樣跌入悲痛，再點樣走出傷痛，同埋親人死前嘅點滴，點樣喺死後仍然影響住佢地。<br />\n<br />\n四個家庭分別係：<br />\n兩兄弟失去咗爸爸嘅<span class=\"red\"><strong><ins>谷口</ins></strong></span>家<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3Q4QBkq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3Q4QBkq.jpg&h=dc896d36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n三姊弟冇咗爸爸嘅<span class=\"gold\"><strong><ins>村上</ins></strong></span>家<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4TzQACb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4TzQACb.jpg&h=5d13bd7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n媽媽失去咗九歲仔仔嘅<span class=\"blue\"><strong><ins>美谷島</ins></strong></span>家<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7zjUiy7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7zjUiy7.jpg&h=2e78b551&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩老失去咗三個女嘅<span class=\"limegreen\"><strong><ins>田淵</ins></strong></span>家<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X5o59F2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX5o59F2.jpg&h=a6c7ac17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n紀錄片用唔少篇幅描寫佢地當年點樣崩潰，但我覺得更重要嘅係佢地點樣走出傷痛，呢個先係段片嘅重點。<br />\n<br />\n兩兄弟冇咗爸爸嘅<strong><span class=\"red\"><ins>谷口</ins></span></strong>家，媽媽本來想自殺，但係被老公遺書嘅「孩子們就拜託你」救返。<br />\n仲因為老公生前同佢講過話佢好適合做生意，決定走出傷痛，出返嚟做野。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mCvXf3u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmCvXf3u.jpg&h=4821b96e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<ins>谷口</ins>而家會拎住本記載住佢地一家四口嘅自撰故事書，去唔同嘅小學分享，希望教小朋友珍惜同感恩。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tCwzizJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtCwzizJ.jpg&h=1a47af3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而三姊弟冇咗爸爸嘅<strong><span class=\"gold\"><ins>村上</ins></span></strong>家，佢地屋企本身唔算有錢，買野要諗過度過，但爸爸知大女<ins>美樹</ins>鍾意睇書，每次買書都由個女買。<br />\n爸爸死咗之後，佢再收唔到爸爸買嘅書，反而係留低嘅書同埋爸爸封遺書，提醒佢活得精彩。<br />\n最後<ins>村上美樹</ins>真係成為咗一個語文老師。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pP9ANth.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpP9ANth.jpg&h=062fe492&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n冇咗九歲仔仔嘅<strong><span class=\"blue\"><ins>美谷島</ins></span></strong>媽媽，成立咗「8.12聯絡會」，希望幫其他同樣受悲傷困擾嘅遇難者家屬。<br />\n聯絡會到而家都仲有好多紀念活動，美谷島喺紀錄片入面亦都講返30年前決定搞聯絡會嘅心路歷程，好值得聽。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cV95p3D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcV95p3D.jpg&h=90f2a8d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家<ins>美谷島邦子</ins>已經走出傷痛，去唔同嘅小學分享仔仔細個嘅故事。<br />\n其實無論係搞聯絡會又好，去小學分享都好，雖然表面上係幫緊人，但我覺得更加係<ins>美谷島</ins>令自己釋懷嘅方法嚟。<br />\n好多人選擇唔提唔面對，一直放喺心，但有勇氣去積極面對，反而可能更幫到自己。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WB3aBmZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWB3aBmZ.jpg&h=cbc10209&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最遲走出傷痛嘅，係冇咗三個女嘅<strong><span class=\"limegreen\"><ins>田淵</ins></span></strong>媽。<br />\n本來滴酒不沾嘅佢，因為受唔住打擊，酗酒足足25年，仲出現精神問題。<br />\n後來有次飲到入廠，佢夢到大女報夢叫佢振作，終於慢慢走出傷痛。三年前紀念活動，已經84歲嘅佢都有出席。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dRsZuj1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdRsZuj1.jpg&h=f096f671&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n三年前係空難33週年，佢地再一次去墜機嗰座山拜屋企人。對佢地嚟講，嗰份掛念無論幾多個33年都唔會減退。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kVcnsux.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkVcnsux.jpg&h=baa5d952&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n冇咗三個女嘅<strong><span class=\"limegreen\"><ins>田淵</ins></span></strong>爸，之前因為要睇住已經徹底崩潰嘅老婆，一直死撐咗卅年，仲要俾老婆鬧佢點解好似唔傷心咁，但其實一直好掛住三個女。<br />\n去到佢地個墓碑前面，就算已經九十歲，就算已經過咗卅年，都即刻忍唔住喊。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7ogjufw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7ogjufw.jpg&h=c51b3087&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另一part好感動嘅，係<strong><span class=\"blue\"><ins>美谷島</ins></span></strong>媽媽話，仔仔喺佢心目中永遠都係九歲嗰個樣。<br />\n節目主持已經51歲，真係阿叔咁，但其實同遇難個小朋友只係爭九年，佢都話如果小朋友未死，佢地而家可以一齊飲酒。<br />\n但媽媽每次拜仔仔嗰陣，放低嘅都係Doraemon。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZsjdyH1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZsjdyH1.jpg&h=a3a588e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\nBtw 班演員真係演得好好，又要演出事之前好無憂嘅生活，又要演出事之後嘅崩潰同聲嘶力竭，仲要係生離死別呢啲沉重課題，而且好多都只係小朋友嚟，但真係演得好好，好容易令人入到戲。<br />\n<br />\n睇完固之然好sad，但見到佢地真係好堅強好積極，同時都會為佢地感到開心。<br />\n家人嘅死，當然令佢地失去咗好多，但係都因為家人嘅死 ，令佢地成為一個更好嘅人。<br />\n<br />\n好似當年13歲個妹妹<strong><span class=\"gold\"><ins>村上</ins></span></strong>咁，一直都記得爸爸死前成日買書俾佢，最後成為咗一個語文老師；<br />\n仲有兩個分別冇咗仔仔同老公嘅女士 &mdash; <span class=\"blue\"><ins><strong>美谷島</strong></ins></span>同<span class=\"red\"><ins><strong>谷口</strong></ins></span>咁，佢地都不約而同，周圍去唔同嘅小學分享，教小朋友要愛惜生命、珍惜身邊嘅人。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n新年流流，咁多生死嘅topic好似好唔match，但希望大家喺呢個節日，睇完都會有特別嘅感受。<br />\n好老土嘅「珍惜眼前人」又好、喺佢地身上參考點樣走出悲傷都好，我相信大家會有得著。<br />\n<br />\n好多謝睇到尾嘅你，希望你鍾意我嘅分享。"},{"pid":"ed45cc700a15b2cdb7e029812527fc216b1e3a81","tid":2406003,"uid":342554,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T07:34:55.000Z","msg":"Pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d40e884886f5967d6f76b8e9fdf41b3dc72cbfc8","tid":2406003,"uid":38777,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T12:09:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e71ca5ffbd41903e7d9b476816107d1a98265cd0","tid":2406003,"uid":1493,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T12:18:32.000Z","msg":"我過完年睇"},{"pid":"19c6acf3554e4a43d47a37168b465d59ecda1477","tid":2406003,"uid":183758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a2858576f7e3dec5c0460fb53e186c3384990c12","tid":2406003,"uid":341313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T00:08:13.000Z","msg":"最近見到有post講日航空難<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2401734\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2401734</a><br />\n之後睇返啲紀錄片 發現呢段做得好好<br />\n睇完真係好心噏 但值得一睇<br />\n因為佢地走出傷痛嘅過程真係好感動<br />\n<br />\n首先請原諒係殘體字幕 但我只係搵到呢條<br />\n其次係如果大家想自己慢慢發掘條片嘅內容 請無視我下面嗰堆介紹 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=z_16HZtfwI0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dz_16HZtfwI0&d=kdQtjCisvz5VKkzPdH2zQ98yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=680a8b7f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=z_16HZtfwI0</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qYIqrRuGUKo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DqYIqrRuGUKo&d=kdQtjCisvz5VKkzPdH2zQ98yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=3511b525\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qYIqrRuGUKo</a><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n段片係用「事故紀錄片+情境重演+三十年後訪問」嘅形式，講返四個遇難者家庭喺出事後33年嘅生活。<br />\n講佢地當年點樣跌入悲痛，再點樣走出傷痛，同埋親人死前嘅點滴，點樣喺死後仍然影響住佢地。<br />\n<br />\n四個家庭分別係：<br />\n兩兄弟失去咗爸爸嘅<span class=\"red\"><strong><ins>谷口</ins></strong></span>家<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3Q4QBkq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3Q4QBkq.jpg&h=dc896d36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n三姊弟冇咗爸爸嘅<span class=\"gold\"><strong><ins>村上</ins></strong></span>家<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4TzQACb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4TzQACb.jpg&h=5d13bd7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n媽媽失去咗九歲仔仔嘅<span class=\"blue\"><strong><ins>美谷島</ins></strong></span>家<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7zjUiy7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7zjUiy7.jpg&h=2e78b551&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩老失去咗三個女嘅<span class=\"limegreen\"><strong><ins>田淵</ins></strong></span>家<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X5o59F2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX5o59F2.jpg&h=a6c7ac17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n紀錄片用唔少篇幅描寫佢地當年點樣崩潰，但我覺得更重要嘅係佢地點樣走出傷痛，呢個先係段片嘅重點。<br />\n<br />\n兩兄弟冇咗爸爸嘅<strong><span class=\"red\"><ins>谷口</ins></span></strong>家，媽媽本來想自殺，但係被老公遺書嘅「孩子們就拜託你」救返。<br />\n仲因為老公生前同佢講過話佢好適合做生意，決定走出傷痛，出返嚟做野。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mCvXf3u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmCvXf3u.jpg&h=4821b96e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<ins>谷口</ins>而家會拎住本記載住佢地一家四口嘅自撰故事書，去唔同嘅小學分享，希望教小朋友珍惜同感恩。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tCwzizJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtCwzizJ.jpg&h=1a47af3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而三姊弟冇咗爸爸嘅<strong><span class=\"gold\"><ins>村上</ins></span></strong>家，佢地屋企本身唔算有錢，買野要諗過度過，但爸爸知大女<ins>美樹</ins>鍾意睇書，每次買書都由個女買。<br />\n爸爸死咗之後，佢再收唔到爸爸買嘅書，反而係留低嘅書同埋爸爸封遺書，提醒佢活得精彩。<br />\n最後<ins>村上美樹</ins>真係成為咗一個語文老師。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pP9ANth.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpP9ANth.jpg&h=062fe492&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n冇咗九歲仔仔嘅<strong><span class=\"blue\"><ins>美谷島</ins></span></strong>媽媽，成立咗「8.12聯絡會」，希望幫其他同樣受悲傷困擾嘅遇難者家屬。<br />\n聯絡會到而家都仲有好多紀念活動，美谷島喺紀錄片入面亦都講返30年前決定搞聯絡會嘅心路歷程，好值得聽。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cV95p3D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcV95p3D.jpg&h=90f2a8d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家<ins>美谷島邦子</ins>已經走出傷痛，去唔同嘅小學分享仔仔細個嘅故事。<br />\n其實無論係搞聯絡會又好，去小學分享都好，雖然表面上係幫緊人，但我覺得更加係<ins>美谷島</ins>令自己釋懷嘅方法嚟。<br />\n好多人選擇唔提唔面對，一直放喺心，但有勇氣去積極面對，反而可能更幫到自己。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WB3aBmZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWB3aBmZ.jpg&h=cbc10209&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最遲走出傷痛嘅，係冇咗三個女嘅<strong><span class=\"limegreen\"><ins>田淵</ins></span></strong>媽。<br />\n本來滴酒不沾嘅佢，因為受唔住打擊，酗酒足足25年，仲出現精神問題。<br />\n後來有次飲到入廠，佢夢到大女報夢叫佢振作，終於慢慢走出傷痛。三年前紀念活動，已經84歲嘅佢都有出席。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dRsZuj1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdRsZuj1.jpg&h=f096f671&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n三年前係空難33週年，佢地再一次去墜機嗰座山拜屋企人。對佢地嚟講，嗰份掛念無論幾多個33年都唔會減退。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kVcnsux.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkVcnsux.jpg&h=baa5d952&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n冇咗三個女嘅<strong><span class=\"limegreen\"><ins>田淵</ins></span></strong>爸，之前因為要睇住已經徹底崩潰嘅老婆，一直死撐咗卅年，仲要俾老婆鬧佢點解好似唔傷心咁，但其實一直好掛住三個女。<br />\n去到佢地個墓碑前面，就算已經九十歲，就算已經過咗卅年，都即刻忍唔住喊。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7ogjufw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7ogjufw.jpg&h=c51b3087&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另一part好感動嘅，係<strong><span class=\"blue\"><ins>美谷島</ins></span></strong>媽媽話，仔仔喺佢心目中永遠都係九歲嗰個樣。<br />\n節目主持已經51歲，真係阿叔咁，但其實同遇難個小朋友只係爭九年，佢都話如果小朋友未死，佢地而家可以一齊飲酒。<br />\n但媽媽每次拜仔仔嗰陣，放低嘅都係Doraemon。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZsjdyH1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZsjdyH1.jpg&h=a3a588e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\nBtw 班演員真係演得好好，又要演出事之前好無憂嘅生活，又要演出事之後嘅崩潰同聲嘶力竭，仲要係生離死別呢啲沉重課題，而且好多都只係小朋友嚟，但真係演得好好，好容易令人入到戲。<br />\n<br />\n睇完固之然好sad，但見到佢地真係好堅強好積極，同時都會為佢地感到開心。<br />\n家人嘅死，當然令佢地失去咗好多，但係都因為家人嘅死 ，令佢地成為一個更好嘅人。<br />\n<br />\n好似當年13歲個妹妹<strong><span class=\"gold\"><ins>村上</ins></span></strong>咁，一直都記得爸爸死前成日買書俾佢，最後成為咗一個語文老師；<br />\n仲有兩個分別冇咗仔仔同老公嘅女士 &mdash; <span class=\"blue\"><ins><strong>美谷島</strong></ins></span>同<span class=\"red\"><ins><strong>谷口</strong></ins></span>咁，佢地都不約而同，周圍去唔同嘅小學分享，教小朋友要愛惜生命、珍惜身邊嘅人。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n新年流流，咁多生死嘅topic好似好唔match，但希望大家喺呢個節日，睇完都會有特別嘅感受。<br />\n好老土嘅「珍惜眼前人」又好、喺佢地身上參考點樣走出悲傷都好，我相信大家會有得著。<br />\n<br />\n好多謝睇到尾嘅你，希望你鍾意我嘅分享。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T12:24:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63a9916a54cc68c4185f714e2d4c972fc50c08de","tid":2406003,"uid":53122,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T12:28:14.000Z","msg":"d單真係最sad<br />\n<br />\n其他空難都一嘢爆死左"},{"pid":"7222492c0e21f9bd282677aa7324bcc822bcf9bb","tid":2406003,"uid":301952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T12:30:06.000Z","msg":"日本加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08ee9513597ac2a0da055e8b5030fd405acdccb2","tid":2406003,"uid":30868,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T12:41:51.000Z","msg":"遲d 睇番"},{"pid":"3b7b1543b11af95f98afb3057eb29fef7e13e380","tid":2406003,"uid":362737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T12:42:49.000Z","msg":"走左三個女個個最慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其他都有仔女扶持住"},{"pid":"26ead3460076d2052ec0452846759e7f968c23ea","tid":2406003,"uid":341313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed45cc700a15b2cdb7e029812527fc216b1e3a81","tid":2406003,"uid":342554,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T07:34:55.000Z","msg":"Pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T14:42:52.000Z","msg":"多謝你 好多謝你幫我推上嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e81ad83b6c76efad7400ca9d7d23b244c46c4901","tid":2406003,"uid":341313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b7b1543b11af95f98afb3057eb29fef7e13e380","tid":2406003,"uid":362737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021